1. *Listi* su počeli da se pojavljuju na drveću. (The leaves have started to appear on the trees.)

2. *Listići* se suše na suncu. (The leaflets are drying in the sun.)

3. *List* je bio prekriven gustim crnim linijama. (The leaf was covered with thick black lines.)

4. Ova biljka ima *listove* sa zaobljenim rubovima. (This plant has leaves with rounded edges.)

5. U parku je mnogo stabala sa zelenim *listićima*. (There are many trees in the park with green leaflets.)

6. Ona je uklonila suvi *list* sa cveta. (She removed a dry leaf from the flower.)

7. U proleće će biti puno zelenih *listova* na drveću. (In the spring there will be many green leaves on the trees.)